snippet.title: SEEN Trailer (Halloween Game Jam)
snippet.description:
FREE DOWNLOAD: https://fatgandalfgames.itch.io/seen   
My game jam entry for #Thenerdmansion #TheHalloweenJam 2023. Rules are simple: 30 day maximum development time, theme is "amalgamation of horror", and the game must contain some references to traditional Halloween monsters such as ghosts, zombies, or vampires. In this game, you are bitten by a vampire and put through a test to prove you are worthy of being reborn as a creature of the night, Saw-style...
